# Common Troubleshooting

```bash
# Enter running container
docker exec -it <container> sh

# Running processes
ps aux

# Current directory
pwd

# List files
ls -la

# Environment variables
env
printenv

# Disk usage
df -h

# Memory usage
free -m

# Test application
wget http://localhost:3000
curl http://localhost:3000

# Check mounted files
mount

# View application logs
docker logs <container>
```

